reviews.text:
Laqué NAILS & BEAUTY is your personal manicure and pedicure studio, more than just self-care...

Laqué is a philosophy of life, therapy for problems, your little key to harmony. We believe that happy girls will save this world, and our task is to give you this joy and reveal all the facets of their beauty.
Always on the move and limited in time? Our craftsmen will make your wishes come true in a matter of minutes – efficiently, safely and for a long time.
Tired of worries? We will help you relax, forget about troubles and maybe even find the right solution. During our treatments, you are immersed in a real paradise for body and soul - relax in Laqué.
Manicure and pedicure are our main services. We work with the best craftsmen and only with premium materials. There are no compromises when it comes to the beauty of our clients.
Our principle is impeccable cleanliness and hygienic safety. Before each client, instruments undergo a multi-stage sterilization system, including a medical autoclave. And all this before your eyes - we have nothing to hide!
As additional offers, we are ready to make your eyebrows and eyelashes perfect, as well as make-up for any occasion and occasion.
Very quickly you will become friends with us, and, like true friends, we will gladly come to the rescue and have fun together. Exclusive mixes from the most fashionable DJs are played only for you in our studio, and on Fridays you can hear them live at our pre-party parties. Master classes, lectures and simply interesting meetings - all this awaits our regular customers.
In addition, we treat all guests to a glass of prosecco or delicious coffee, which can also be enjoyed on our cozy terrace with a magnificent view of the Botanical Garden. And for this you don’t have to do any procedure with us, just come and visit us - we are always glad to see you.
